# English UI copy

- All user-visible strings in pages and components (headings, body text, labels, tooltips, example data shown in the design charter) must be in **English**.
- Match existing project style: this app uses **British English** for design terms where already established (e.g. *colour*).
- **Do not** add French or other languages for UI explanations or placeholder card fields (titles of real works may stay in the original language).
- When adding or editing copy, prefer clear, concise technical writing consistent with the design-charter tone.
